thread.title: Fresca

author: Fresca
title: Fresca
text: Never had a problem with booking tickets with them. I like how they don't try to force feed you the extras like travel insurance and car rental. Sometimes the price you pay is a few pounds more than the initial price Quote: d to you. I just paid an extra £6 more for a plane ticket but that may be due to exchange rates and it's a small extra price for a plane ticket that's £100 cheaper than what I would get on the airline website.
